title.content-text: 3.5.3 - V LAN Support for IP Telephony and Wireless

brief.content-text:
The diagram depicts a router, labeled R1, at the top of a star topology with two switches, labeled S1 and S2.
Directly connected to S1 are the following devices: V LAN 18 - DATA, V LAN 17 - VOICE, V LAN 35 - Wireless.
Directly connected to S2 are the following devices: V LAN 18 - DATA, V LAN 17 - VOICE, V LAN 35 - Wireless.
